Zero point energy                ...      0.75203099 Eh     471.91 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.04418264 Eh      27.72 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
Thermal translational correction ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Total thermal energy                  -3124.50303136 Eh


